  "sentences": [
    {
      "id": "u11-s1",
      "text": "Have you ever noticed a monster around us?",
      "paragraphId": "u11-p1",
      "keywords": [
        "noticed",
        "monster",
        "around"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-s2",
      "text": "It's not big or scary, but it's very dangerous.",
      "paragraphId": "u11-p1",
      "keywords": [
        "scary",
        "dangerous"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-s3",
      "text": "This monster comes in many forms – games, social media and TV shows.",
      "paragraphId": "u11-p1",
      "keywords": [
        "forms",
        "games",
        "social media",
        "TV shows"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-s4",
      "text": "You may ask, “It brings us so much fun. So why do you say it's a monster?”",
      "paragraphId": "u11-p1",
      "keywords": [
        "brings",
        "fun",
        "monster"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-s5",
      "text": "At first, we may all think, \"I'll just have a little fun.\"",
      "paragraphId": "u11-p2",
      "keywords": [
        "at first",
        "think",
        "little fun"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-s6",
      "text": "We turn on the computer and start a game.",
      "paragraphId": "u11-p2",
      "keywords": [
        "turn on",
        "computer",
        "start",
        "game"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-s7",
      "text": "But soon the monster takes over.",
      "paragraphId": "u11-p2",
      "keywords": [
        "soon",
        "monster",
        "takes over"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-s8",
      "text": "It starts to eat away our time, minute by minute.",
      "paragraphId": "u11-p2",
      "keywords": [
        "starts",
        "eat away",
        "time",
        "minute by minute"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-s9",
      "text": "But we just sit there and look at the screen without noticing it at all.",
      "paragraphId": "u11-p3",
      "keywords": [
        "sit",
        "look",
        "screen",
        "noticing"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-s10",
      "text": "We often get lost in the monster's world like this.",
      "paragraphId": "u11-p3",
      "keywords": [
        "get lost",
        "monster's world"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-s11",
      "text": "We become couch potatoes with sore necks and dry eyes.",
      "paragraphId": "u11-p3",
      "keywords": [
        "become",
        "couch potatoes",
        "sore necks",
        "dry eyes"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-s12",
      "text": "We miss out on sweet moments with loved ones.",
      "paragraphId": "u11-p4",
      "keywords": [
        "miss out",
        "sweet moments",
        "loved ones"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-s13",
      "text": "We are deaf to the real world.",
      "paragraphId": "u11-p4",
      "keywords": [
        "deaf",
        "real world"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-s14",
      "text": "Just remember, too much fun also makes Jack a dull boy!",
      "paragraphId": "u11-p5",
      "keywords": [
        "remember",
        "too much fun",
        "dull boy"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-s15",
      "text": "The time-eating monster will always be there.",
      "paragraphId": "u11-p5",
      "keywords": [
        "time-eating monster",
        "always",
        "there"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-s16",
      "text": "But we can keep it away by having fun in a balanced way.",
      "paragraphId": "u11-p5",
      "keywords": [
        "keep away",
        "balanced way"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-s17",
      "text": "So, stand up and leave the screens!",
      "paragraphId": "u11-p5",
      "keywords": [
        "stand up",
        "leave",
        "screens"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-s18",
      "text": "Go outside, feel the sun on your face, and jog in the fresh air.",
      "paragraphId": "u11-p5",
      "keywords": [
        "go outside",
        "feel",
        "sun",
        "jog",
        "fresh air"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-s19",
      "text": "Play tennis or go hiking with your friends.",
      "paragraphId": "u11-p5",
      "keywords": [
        "play tennis",
        "go hiking",
        "friends"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-s20",
      "text": "Talk about your day with your family.",
      "paragraphId": "u11-p5",
      "keywords": [
        "talk about",
        "day",
        "family"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-s21",
      "text": "There is so much for you to do.",
      "paragraphId": "u11-p5",
      "keywords": [
        "so much",
        "do"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u11-s22",
      "text": "The choice is ours.",
      "paragraphId": "u11-p5",
      "keywords": [
        "choice",
        "ours"
      ]
    }
  ],
